import Icon from '@chakra-ui/icon'
import { HStack } from '@chakra-ui/layout'
import React from 'react'
import { FaFacebookF, FaTwitter, FaGoogle, FaSpotify, FaShopify } from 'react-icons/fa'

function Social() {
    return (
        <HStack spacing="24">
            <Icon as={FaTwitter} style={{cursor: 'pointer'}} boxSize="50" 
            onClick={() =>
                        window.open("https://twitter.com/LakshyaMishra56")}
             />
            <Icon as={FaGoogle} boxSize="50" />
            <Icon as={FaSpotify} boxSize="50" />
            <Icon as={FaShopify} boxSize="50" />
        </HStack>
    )
}

export default Social
